            , was indicted for <rs id="t17990403-10-off55" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17990403-10-off55" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17990403-10-off55" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17990403-10-cd56" type="crimeDate">27th of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17990403-10-off55 t17990403-10-cd56"></join>, seventy pounds of ground sugar, value 50s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17990403-10-victim149" type="victimName">
                     Augustus 
                     Stevens
                  <interp inst="t17990403-10-victim149" type="surname" value="Stevens"></interp>
